extracted_text:
J) CS-MU Cedar Street Mixed-Use District.
Purpose: The reason for this district is to protect, enhance and guide the redevelopment of the
Cedar Street corridor by reducing visual clutter through the implementation of commercial
design standards and selecting the appropriate type of uses for this district. These standards are
designed to improve the aesthetics, traffic congestion and provide for a solid and vibrant tax
base as well as promote the public health, safety and welfare of the town.
